Justice Oluwatoyin Taiwo of the Ikeja Special Offences Court has granted bail in the sum of two million naira and two sureties to Nollywood actor Olarenwaju Oyiminka popularly known as alias Baba Ijesha. The judge on Thursday ordered that one of the sureties be a blood relative of the defendant and the other, a lawyer. Recall that Baba IIjesha is facing a six-count charge bordering on the indecent treatment of a child, sexual assault, attempted sexual assault by penetration and sexual assault by penetration. Details shortly â€¦